- Proprietary tools and platform partnerships: OMG Impact (media ESG index) and Omnicom’s own environmental data platform (Credera partnership) are useful proprietary/commercial tools that show innovation in measurement and client offerings [omg](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFfmK_wWtYYx4qs5u3pAbcCl5XFfHa9jz2ADLeBEHOKp0V0u_N2QV9iLVrMIJdb5uKZSYDWVcc8BHIKZ_zng5uQlGSOOFSJ8WvgCXT84B3w59WyzKOQmVQo3H63brGUNOAueWo3AQsBtgk=) [credera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE8IqfhW7c4l9POXwruYVZzNJqSxV7d2e7G50e7BqfFk73KsIOwCRyI-4Nk3UiLPKEBbmOIsr0A1mdWq6ITkmwAjRnzU2R7xCWaEuQKASfZ3nliO363Z6yRghMhiFAxv7FO2-M3d6dP9qrAy0UgG_9BJZB4eehcJ3KwtAkA6qKpab_KEGpEDbS1MFFt5pqh6wxlv5WX3URH9papGpjCbSzFLYxvT7Vk_Trb6T9tCd8=) [themedialeader](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEMjC30W4BNdz3Z0S4up8EWkoba0GJ_WpOZoKnDc-KNZ-nAAE3I-dVpy80kCtaYAZkjY-RnK3tMiZHJsQtIGKi1ZlZaRjwa95czu3dMOk427dUjJkNHCunBEVSCN2jokuJb8TmTTG4Bz58Ad_97jyBpHGf7QkESS0v9RsRgfI4_IEKq6PMwLNpA1X3yu87YQ2WuforhI05s).
