Why 16/25: Omnicom demonstrates a solid innovation program in sustainability measurement and client-facing ESG tooling, with meaningful partnerships. It is not, however, documented as investing heavily in proprietary climate‑technology R&D, breakthrough low‑carbon patents, or major energy‑generation innovations — so it is strong but not an innovation leader in climate tech.

