- Formal targets and governance: SBTi‑validated 2030 target (46.2% absolute reduction), Chief Environmental Sustainability Officer in place (Karen van Bergen) leading the program, monthly Environmental Sustainability Global Core Team meetings — all indicate concrete governance and targets [omnicomgroup](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQExwQrY1uuIjm_vbWIjOS62_GQDtlHA5M4ZcTcG-yGCz4KpOIiJFAyX1NiPSjy3RQfRf3mqwgPd99LZb0QKzcI5eYynu3uOSQuA0KcFRYjVFqDUDSsJ5Gv7NhnZgPGJPp7WpW8lucJFI15uFyaY7dh1dl86I1CvG44MUT9lhW_Bbm5QhUoZP6ciNlhRGAWI7oIYmdRE) [esgtoday](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFtx_5VvqkIsRzPlzSQn3iBwhBKi00_plNV8ytsqFslFJcoHs4sElSEr6_1BLc7VnDDi2EvF284swYTM2r1WDmSQR1WaRrFt80m47rnwGo0TQqTXvtNymNE0vBGDtGBGShHmQB4wfgsRIx8ASiT5CPct2dmVa6x6hRN77u9TGcrh3mwgdqS6M_CBKCGpyVU7VzPG9EbrQ==) [omnicomgroup](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE5-yJKjYJBF3pqlb4gxe7BoXiPOGmK9QXhnbDgvSNM0JoQTMtxcsudW6u2rcNXls1UOaWP7UypIfvifaiSdHZLlZk8kMyG6ip4eekioLB2Ej2wSpFHU0bbI3l6B0QTk0pRjGaql_JpxQwnCKho_7WcrnvYEvgzCkcZSQ6-7-izdvLF7O8vgRY=).
