- Omnicom has invested in digital and GenAI capabilities (Omni 3.0) and continues data and analytics investments, which have sustainability efficiency potential but are not primarily climate tech [q4cdn](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGs7AzhNFb7Zoq6Lap3cIDud1go4EiFrptjfGTS4igu8GCGDUXsUmBIb__6jonEFkm0PKK2DkXflNsLAnGjY2_Mtwviszek0Eb0EBUsgMMnTF9yW-3Nip2EBQH_OTRMVX0CgMoT-0_CDaB9CIK8FkeUct5XfODA830CqUUS_iTFTG7cgeeFVyWuHSF6SDOlUA44Ed408rjQ-UiGwppPL8Q6bmYTqXRtVCk=) [dcfmodeling](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHqH9d6m7KotMGz_bGt9bOXDXP1FusVjHL3NCxbLgiBOKe4yC-MA37HOFg56uCKY4VCWQ-42W6oXEQdp91kqXwP3V6jWMVdH55yhw74jcIBiI85aNjJuWV3t5ZETOI4bdfat_upxDvTdM-4PPXwbZG0PVA=).

Recommendations (brief)
- Accelerate large‑scale renewable procurement disclosure (volume/percentage, PPAs) and set explicit year‑by‑year renewable electricity targets to move from “seeking to purchase” to demonstrable contracted coverage. (Peers have clearer renewable targets.) [wpp](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGXWJpc1bVHVS1ADi8k4Zt6OEamQQi1yeljnbIs2F1TfMrRIf1rNwYmcm3VDovsSm8nP0pTAZJX3ES5EDStT8sTGDTs4dehmQr33323ZV5lZQmvglgpqnK6nAbfnoS47u0Kac8SgezOFgP_jRw1BbygabY=) [publicisgroupe](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEVFWHiXBXCzBlu5ZWo0wI9nJe79dkVkBDYeI2LnpdAUtLxNeuvlAXNRM-253xY-_zBZHCb8XUzJ6e3tLl7boHv83fJ9-XjSe3klG4NRn12YDL_KVpCCc1MM0MzGpU_ZPsmQOUG5YJSZdD0LQ-a9mkL_3PcNaMHtdVQM_KLVPMeYeEMKd6ablkbr7kADh0ElRTlEIyQ)
- Publish a detailed technology roadmap for fleet electrification, building retrofits (BMS/HVAC/LED), and targeted Scope‑3 interventions (business travel reduction plans) with KPIs and timelines to close Scope 1 and 3 gaps [omnicomgroup](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGEvoWeY-yq1gUr9nSqLfn1GFkCbrk40CAbt33pkS2MW0QAuJCWo38Hkqhnpb89Ar2DKqnX0ur-p4GOKrMPbf6lZI3YRnD8B5HhUJuxQrBxnA-ky_OJlgaJXb58djIAdLaGpkiTn_veW1IjO70oqFv_OGKpTKBDh6Sek-TdO9OJdneypSeIwSphpUnNe26KUXiZqaqD).
- Scale client‑facing ESG tech (e.g., expand OMG Impact capabilities globally) and package commercial sustainability services to monetize the measurement tools while driving media‑supply chain reductions [omg](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFfmK_wWtYYx4qs5u3pAbcCl5XFfHa9jz2ADLeBEHOKp0V0u_N2QV9iLVrMIJdb5uKZSYDWVcc8BHIKZ_zng5uQlGSOOFSJ8WvgCXT84B3w59WyzKOQmVQo3H63brGUNOAueWo3AQsBtgk=) [themedialeader](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEMjC30W4BNdz3Z0S4up8EWkoba0GJ_WpOZoKnDc-KNZ-nAAE3I-dVpy80kCtaYAZkjY-RnK3tMiZHJsQtIGKi1ZlZaRjwa95czu3dMOk427dUjJkNHCunBEVSCN2jokuJb8TmTTG4Bz58Ad_97jyBpHGf7QkESS0v9RsRgfI4_IEKq6PMwLNpA1X3yu87YQ2WuforhI05s).

